Yek '''Lakh''' ([[Bangla]]: লাখ) si yek gin le [[Desi Ginavipennaskro sestemi]] prinjardo kay [[Bharat]], [[Bangladesh]], [[Pakistan]], [[Shri Lanka]], [[Myanmar]]. Yek Lakh si [[100000|yek shel Seriya]] (10<sup>5</sup>). Yek Shel Lakh si yek [[Kror]] vay desh Miliyonurya.

Kadava Ginavipen thol xulavitorya pe aver thana sar avryal i [[Sudutni Asiya]]. Sar misalyake, 30 Lakh (3 Miliyonurya) Lekhavdyovel sar 30,00,000 chi 3,000,000.

Kadava Gin si vi andi [[Svahili Chib]], navyardo ''Lakhi''. Pe Chorengi Chib andar [[Mumbai]] phenel pes ''Peti''.

Kay [[Gaudiya Vaishnava|Bangla Vayshnava]] yek Lakh si o divesutno acharuno bashavipen le [[Hari|Hareske]] nava [http://wiki.gaudiyakutir.com/Lakh]; le duma ''Yek Lakh nava'' janglyoven but.

